1
00:00:18,560 --> 00:00:23,430
[Zhizi Alley]

2
00:00:27,670 --> 00:00:28,760
What are we eating tonight?

3
00:00:28,760 --> 00:00:30,320
Bin, you're still thinking about food?

4
00:00:30,320 --> 00:00:31,280
Look at how fat you are.

5
00:00:31,280 --> 00:00:32,670
Your fat jiggles when you walk.

6
00:00:32,670 --> 00:00:32,960
No,

7
00:00:32,960 --> 00:00:34,280
I'm starving.

8
00:00:34,350 --> 00:00:36,110
Finish what's in your mouth first,

9
00:00:36,110 --> 00:00:37,600
then look at your big belly.

10
00:00:37,600 --> 00:00:39,070
All he's thinking about
is that he's hungry,

11
00:00:39,070 --> 00:00:39,920
you know?

12
00:00:40,110 --> 00:00:41,240
Alright, that's enough.

13
00:00:41,240 --> 00:00:42,920
It's quite bouncy, though.

14
00:00:58,000 --> 00:00:58,930
Jiang Hansheng,

15
00:00:59,280 --> 00:01:00,150
hurry up!

16
00:01:01,470 --> 00:01:03,670
Why are you always so slow?

17
00:01:19,640 --> 00:01:20,590
Jiang Hansheng!

18
00:01:20,950 --> 00:01:22,150
Hurry up!

19
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:24,560
What are you looking at?

20
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:25,950
This is no longer your home.

21
00:01:25,950 --> 00:01:27,120
The car has been waiting outside
for a long time.

22
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:27,950
Let's go.

23
00:01:32,070 --> 00:01:33,670
Say hello to Auntie Xiaoruo.

24
00:01:33,850 --> 00:01:35,009
Hello, Hansheng.

25
00:01:35,430 --> 00:01:36,360
Say hello to her.

26
00:01:36,430 --> 00:01:37,030
It's fine.

27
00:01:37,479 --> 00:01:38,280
This child...

28
00:01:38,570 --> 00:01:39,650
It's okay. We can

29
00:01:39,860 --> 00:01:40,740
talk in the car.

30
00:01:41,050 --> 00:01:42,220
Let's go. Hurry.

31
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:44,039
Bozhi.

32
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:45,280
Let's go!

33
00:01:46,220 --> 00:01:47,350
I don't want to move.

34
00:01:50,550 --> 00:01:51,500
Hansheng,

35
00:01:52,220 --> 00:01:53,620
this house has been sold.

36
00:01:53,630 --> 00:01:54,840
You have to move.

37
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:55,789
Can't you buy it back?

38
00:01:55,789 --> 00:01:57,759
You know my new company

39
00:01:57,759 --> 00:01:58,710
is far from here.

40
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:00,310
When Xiaoruo and I come back at night,

41
00:02:00,310 --> 00:02:01,750
there's no place to park.

42
00:02:01,780 --> 00:02:02,590
We're moving to a

43
00:02:02,590 --> 00:02:04,280
bigger and better place, right?

44
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,440
Let's go. Hurry up.

45
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:07,440
I don't want to go.

46
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,520
Jiang Hansheng,

47
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:13,440
before you turn 18,

48
00:02:13,440 --> 00:02:14,630
I have an obligation to raise you.

49
00:02:14,630 --> 00:02:15,790
When you turn 18

50
00:02:15,790 --> 00:02:16,990
and you're a grownup,

51
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:17,720
where you want to live

52
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:18,870
and who you want to be with

53
00:02:18,870 --> 00:02:19,870
will no longer be my business.

54
00:02:19,870 --> 00:02:21,220
So you have to come with me now.

55
00:02:21,220 --> 00:02:21,750
Let's go.

56
00:02:23,100 --> 00:02:23,440
Okay, okay.

57
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:24,160
What's wrong with you?

58
00:02:24,160 --> 00:02:24,750
Okay, okay.

59
00:02:24,750 --> 00:02:26,560
Don't be angry. Let me talk to him.

60
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:27,240
Hansheng,

61
00:02:27,590 --> 00:02:28,840
just come with us.

62
00:02:29,350 --> 00:02:30,440
We will be

63
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:31,720
a family from now on, right?

64
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:32,790
Living together,

65
00:02:32,820 --> 00:02:33,750
we can take care of each other.

66
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:34,940
I'm used to living alone.

67
00:02:34,940 --> 00:02:36,740
I don't like being taken care of.

68
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:39,240
You're used to living alone
and don't like being taken care of?

69
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,590
You think you're all grown up now, huh?

70
00:02:40,590 --> 00:02:41,120
Fine.

71
00:02:41,150 --> 00:02:42,640
You can live here alone.

72
00:02:42,660 --> 00:02:44,190
Let's see if you can stay until next month

73
00:02:44,190 --> 00:02:46,120
without being kicked out by the new owner.

74
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:46,790
Okay?

75
00:02:47,490 --> 00:02:48,630
Let's go. He won't go, but we will.

76
00:02:48,630 --> 00:02:49,590
Let's go.

77
00:02:50,210 --> 00:02:51,170
Hurry. Let's go.

78
00:02:51,350 --> 00:02:52,280
Leave him alone.

79
00:02:52,790 --> 00:02:53,960
This child...

80
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,570
You're covered in rain.

81
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:16,790
Slow down.

82
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,400
There's a puddle.

83
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:56,390
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

84
00:04:56,750 --> 00:04:59,190
[Episode 17]

85
00:05:19,420 --> 00:05:19,980
Dahua.

86
00:05:20,220 --> 00:05:21,340
Pack up, let's go.

87
00:05:21,980 --> 00:05:23,310
We're finally leaving.

88
00:06:04,070 --> 00:06:05,200
Still the old rules.

89
00:06:19,780 --> 00:06:21,040
What's the situation?

90
00:06:27,930 --> 00:06:29,710
If you don't want me to end up like Yao,

91
00:06:29,710 --> 00:06:31,770
clear out the mole in your team first.

92
00:06:32,350 --> 00:06:33,000
Chief Tan,

93
00:06:33,630 --> 00:06:34,920
your previous suspicions

94
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:36,159
have been confirmed.

95
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:39,310
Jiang Cheng knows
our one-way contact method.

96
00:06:39,310 --> 00:06:40,360
After we met,

97
00:06:40,750 --> 00:06:41,680
he didn't make any

98
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,830
moves against us.

99
00:06:43,270 --> 00:06:44,930
He told us to search for moles.

100
00:06:45,510 --> 00:06:46,770
He really is Cangfeng.

101
00:06:47,310 --> 00:06:48,830
If he really is Cangfeng,

102
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:51,720
why did he use this rare opportunity

103
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:53,870
to only leave this one sentence?

104
00:06:56,159 --> 00:06:57,240
He saw Zhou Jin,

105
00:06:57,510 --> 00:06:59,420
and that's why he was willing to say this.

106
00:06:59,420 --> 00:07:00,350
Among everyone,

107
00:07:00,390 --> 00:07:02,250
the one he trusts the most
must be Zhou Jin.

108
00:07:02,250 --> 00:07:04,710
If it were someone else
in front of him today,

109
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:07,130
he probably wouldn't even have said that.

110
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,010
They dare to deal drugs,

111
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:13,680
which means their situation
is basically stable.

112
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:15,540
They have reason to be confident.

113
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:17,660
Let's not break this confidence.

114
00:07:18,190 --> 00:07:19,570
Once we alert the opponent,

115
00:07:19,570 --> 00:07:21,030
variables will multiply,

116
00:07:21,110 --> 00:07:23,640
and it will only increase
our own difficulty.

117
00:07:25,070 --> 00:07:27,000
We need to find the internal crack,

118
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:29,090
but we can't completely fill it in.

119
00:07:29,270 --> 00:07:30,630
We still need to leave him

120
00:07:30,630 --> 00:07:32,750
time and space to contact the outside,

121
00:07:32,750 --> 00:07:35,080
creating an illusion of going unnoticed.

122
00:07:35,159 --> 00:07:35,890
We could even

123
00:07:36,270 --> 00:07:37,560
use this person

124
00:07:37,830 --> 00:07:39,480
to pass information in reverse

125
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,480
and confuse them.

126
00:07:42,210 --> 00:07:43,570
Professor Jiang,

127
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,830
your idea is good,

128
00:07:47,190 --> 00:07:49,320
but the problem is how to implement it.

129
00:07:50,530 --> 00:07:52,260
And if we don't find the mole,

130
00:07:52,820 --> 00:07:54,240
how can we make Jiang Cheng believe

131
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,700
that we found this person?

132
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:57,780
Won't it threaten his operation?

133
00:07:59,040 --> 00:07:59,900
That's an idea.

134
00:08:00,750 --> 00:08:02,480
We need to let Jiang Cheng know.

135
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,620
-How about this?
-Mentor.

136
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:24,160
This should work.

137
00:08:26,430 --> 00:08:27,030
Chief Tan,

138
00:08:28,270 --> 00:08:29,750
how much have you narrowed down

139
00:08:29,750 --> 00:08:31,280
your previous suspicions?

140
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:36,100
The ones who first knew

141
00:08:36,679 --> 00:08:39,480
that Leader Yao
personally participated in the operation

142
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,679
are mainly these few.

143
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:46,090
[Liu Liang]

144
00:08:46,540 --> 00:08:47,450
[Lu Pengfei]

145
00:08:49,650 --> 00:08:50,590
[Zhao Ping]

146
00:08:51,270 --> 00:08:52,270
These few people.

147
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:56,550
Also,

148
00:08:57,820 --> 00:08:59,880
Professor Jiang, didn't you undergo

149
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,910
the investigation team's interrogation?

150
00:09:01,910 --> 00:09:03,360
Now, I can tell you

151
00:09:04,390 --> 00:09:06,750
this interrogation was jointly planned

152
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:10,170
with my superiors.

153
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,960
The main purpose was to evaluate

154
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:14,150
all those who participated
in the operation.

155
00:09:14,150 --> 00:09:14,870
But

156
00:09:16,790 --> 00:09:18,650
the results were disappointing.

157
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:22,150
The problem is right beside us.

158
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:23,690
Understood.

159
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:26,080
Since there was an interrogation,

160
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:27,440
it can be considered that

161
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,440
personality tests

162
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:31,030
and observations of speech and behavior
have already been done.

163
00:09:31,030 --> 00:09:32,490
Then we can go ahead and use

164
00:09:32,550 --> 00:09:33,790
a fake case

165
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:35,870
to force the mole to show up.

166
00:09:36,550 --> 00:09:37,750
A fake case?

167
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:40,870
Fabricate

168
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:42,630
an operation against Old Scorpion.

169
00:09:42,630 --> 00:09:44,690
An absolutely successful operation

170
00:09:44,970 --> 00:09:46,380
to make him panic.

171
00:09:49,590 --> 00:09:50,190
Chief Tan.

172
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:51,870
Besides Zhou Jin,

173
00:09:52,270 --> 00:09:53,870
who else in the Nancheng Branch

174
00:09:53,870 --> 00:09:55,070
do you trust the most?

175
00:09:57,870 --> 00:09:58,480
Wan.

176
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,200
Wan Chongshan.

177
00:10:00,670 --> 00:10:02,000
He is absolutely clean.

178
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:02,870
Okay.

179
00:10:03,510 --> 00:10:04,310
Then I suggest

180
00:10:04,510 --> 00:10:05,480
you, Zhou Jin,

181
00:10:05,670 --> 00:10:06,630
and Wan Chongshan

182
00:10:06,630 --> 00:10:08,030
lead three teams separately

183
00:10:08,030 --> 00:10:09,360
and act independently.

184
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:11,450
At the beginning of the operation,

185
00:10:11,450 --> 00:10:12,980
when he's still in the dark,

186
00:10:13,390 --> 00:10:15,790
cut off his chances
to contact the outside.

187
00:10:15,910 --> 00:10:17,370
Separate the three people

188
00:10:17,370 --> 00:10:18,870
and, in three different places,

189
00:10:18,870 --> 00:10:21,440
each successfully bust
Old Scorpion's drug deal.

190
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:22,440
Before and after,

191
00:10:22,670 --> 00:10:23,670
they must report,

192
00:10:23,670 --> 00:10:24,390
ask,

193
00:10:24,720 --> 00:10:25,670
and confirm.

194
00:10:28,390 --> 00:10:29,030
Finally,

195
00:10:30,180 --> 00:10:31,510
the ideal situation will be

196
00:10:31,510 --> 00:10:34,560
that Old Scorpion's side will
get a set of information.

197
00:10:34,560 --> 00:10:36,360
As long as Jiang Cheng knows,
he will understand

198
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:37,600
that it's our doing.

199
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:39,080
But he might not know

200
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:40,080
what we are doing,

201
00:10:40,630 --> 00:10:42,030
so he will be anxious too.

202
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:44,120
Normally,

203
00:10:44,630 --> 00:10:46,430
he will contact us proactively.

204
00:10:46,790 --> 00:10:49,200
We can use Jiang Cheng's feedback

205
00:10:49,730 --> 00:10:50,930
to lock onto the mole.

206
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:52,790
Three cars

207
00:10:53,260 --> 00:10:56,260
going to three places
to catch three groups of people.

208
00:10:56,270 --> 00:10:57,140
Whichever car's information

209
00:10:57,140 --> 00:10:58,660
gets to Old Scorpion,

210
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:00,030
that car

211
00:11:00,420 --> 00:11:01,680
will have the suspect.

212
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:03,630
But

213
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:05,940
we'll need Jiang Cheng to tell us.

214
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:07,150
The problem is...

215
00:11:08,790 --> 00:11:11,320
Can he have
such tacit understanding with us?

216
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:13,510
If not,

217
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:16,380
either his ability is questionable,

218
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:18,170
or his stance is questionable.

219
00:11:18,870 --> 00:11:19,870
This is also a test

220
00:11:20,510 --> 00:11:22,570
of whether Jiang Cheng is on our side.

221
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:27,040
Chief Tan.

222
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:28,360
I suggest

223
00:11:28,870 --> 00:11:31,080
everyone participates in this operation.

224
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:32,360
In this operation,

225
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:35,000
don't let the mole feel targeted.

226
00:11:36,600 --> 00:11:37,660
Not only this time.

227
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:39,810
Don't touch this person

228
00:11:40,120 --> 00:11:41,650
until we can close the case.

229
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:44,000
He might be useful in the future.

230
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:46,030
I understand.

231
00:11:47,550 --> 00:11:49,350
As long as we figure out who it is,

232
00:11:50,270 --> 00:11:51,930
we'll just guard against him.

233
00:12:32,420 --> 00:12:34,250
The following meeting
will contain classified information.

234
00:12:34,250 --> 00:12:35,390
Everyone, hand in your phones.

235
00:12:35,390 --> 00:12:36,990
You can turn off your phones.

236
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:47,370
Let me make introductions.

237
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:49,720
This is the SWAT team's

238
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:51,100
Deputy Captain Huang.

239
00:12:51,550 --> 00:12:53,350
From the evening into the night,

240
00:12:53,790 --> 00:12:55,240
we and the SWAT team

241
00:12:55,750 --> 00:12:56,960
might have

242
00:12:57,540 --> 00:12:59,270
an emergency joint operation.

243
00:12:59,510 --> 00:13:00,790
I said "might have"

244
00:13:01,030 --> 00:13:02,790
because the current informant's report

245
00:13:02,790 --> 00:13:04,050
is still unconfirmed.

246
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:05,840
According to our intelligence,

247
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:06,630
there is

248
00:13:07,150 --> 00:13:09,910
an impending illegal transaction
in Haizhou,

249
00:13:10,150 --> 00:13:11,810
most likely involving drugs.

250
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:14,200
As for whether it's related to
the previous case,

251
00:13:14,200 --> 00:13:15,330
we can't be sure yet.

252
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:17,440
So, given our branch's understanding

253
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:19,910
of Old Scorpion crime syndicate,

254
00:13:20,270 --> 00:13:21,070
our superiors

255
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:22,240
ordered us

256
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:24,770
to participate
in this emergency operation.

257
00:13:24,790 --> 00:13:26,870
At the same time, we might also get some

258
00:13:26,870 --> 00:13:28,330
leads about the suspects.

259
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:30,910
Okay, here,

260
00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:32,750
I want to emphasize something.

261
00:13:32,750 --> 00:13:33,750
From now on,

262
00:13:34,630 --> 00:13:35,760
everything you hear

263
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:36,750
and see

264
00:13:36,960 --> 00:13:37,960
is confidential.

265
00:13:38,150 --> 00:13:39,480
Strictly no disclosing

266
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:40,790
or leaking information.

267
00:13:40,790 --> 00:13:41,510
Understood?

268
00:13:41,510 --> 00:13:42,390
-Understood!
-Understood!

269
00:13:42,390 --> 00:13:42,960
Good.

270
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:44,150
Next,

271
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:45,600
Deputy Captain Huang

272
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:48,530
will brief everyone
on the operational deployment.

273
00:13:49,550 --> 00:13:50,550
Hello, everyone.

274
00:13:50,600 --> 00:13:51,670
I am Huang Weixin.

275
00:13:52,630 --> 00:13:54,630
Tonight's emergency joint operation

276
00:13:54,630 --> 00:13:56,120
is under my command.

277
00:13:56,510 --> 00:13:58,970
First, I'll divide the 12 of you
into groups.

278
00:14:13,700 --> 00:14:14,830
I don't know you all.

279
00:14:15,030 --> 00:14:17,430
Please say "here"
when your name is called.

280
00:14:19,870 --> 00:14:20,470
Group One.

281
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,270
-Lu Pengfei.
-Here.

282
00:14:22,850 --> 00:14:24,210
-Qi Jiayuan.
-Here.

283
00:14:24,540 --> 00:14:25,740
-Li Lei.
-Here.

284
00:14:26,180 --> 00:14:27,840
You three take car number one.

285
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:28,960
Professor Jiang.

286
00:14:29,870 --> 00:14:31,270
Group Two. Wan Chongshan.

287
00:14:31,270 --> 00:14:32,080
How is it?

288
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:33,300
-Liu Liang.
-Here.

289
00:14:33,510 --> 00:14:34,790
-Zhang Huilin.
-Here.

