577
00:31:29,550 --> 00:31:30,950
There's major progress.

578
00:31:38,020 --> 00:31:38,820
You know what,

579
00:31:39,780 --> 00:31:41,310
smelling this mountain air

580
00:31:41,440 --> 00:31:42,640
is quite refreshing.

581
00:31:43,770 --> 00:31:44,790
It smells like medicine.

582
00:31:44,790 --> 00:31:45,790
I don't like it.

583
00:31:56,390 --> 00:31:58,640
[Real-time Data Analysis
of the Public Security Bureau]

584
00:31:57,600 --> 00:31:59,200
They've entered Kuangshan.

585
00:32:01,880 --> 00:32:03,920
Many areas in Kuangshan
are primary forests.

586
00:32:03,920 --> 00:32:05,510
Following this route up,

587
00:32:05,600 --> 00:32:06,510
the only habitable places

588
00:32:06,510 --> 00:32:08,530
are Maohe Village and Yatou Village.

589
00:32:08,530 --> 00:32:10,410
Neither village has large populations,

590
00:32:10,410 --> 00:32:12,270
only 40 to 50 households in total.

591
00:32:12,950 --> 00:32:14,380
Within a three-kilometer radius,

592
00:32:14,380 --> 00:32:15,930
there are
six medicinal herb processing plants

593
00:32:15,930 --> 00:32:17,390
and some small workshops.

594
00:32:18,890 --> 00:32:20,350
They are producing drugs.

595
00:32:20,480 --> 00:32:23,680
A pharmaceutical factory
is the best cover for a drug lab.

596
00:33:01,370 --> 00:33:02,660
They changed from driving to walking,

597
00:33:02,660 --> 00:33:04,060
it should be around here.

598
00:33:04,840 --> 00:33:06,120
It really is the medicine factory?

599
00:33:06,120 --> 00:33:07,120
Kuangshan West,

600
00:33:08,370 --> 00:33:10,170
Yatou Pharmaceutical Factory.

601
00:33:17,450 --> 00:33:21,230
[Yatou Pharmaceutical Factory]

602
00:33:30,170 --> 00:33:31,490
The superiors have approved

603
00:33:31,490 --> 00:33:33,250
the decision to conduct

604
00:33:33,270 --> 00:33:34,880
secret investigations

605
00:33:35,030 --> 00:33:36,480
and strike operations against

606
00:33:36,480 --> 00:33:37,640
the possible drug factory
in Kuangshan West.

607
00:33:37,640 --> 00:33:40,350
This operation will be jointly led by
Deputy Commander Liu Zishan

608
00:33:40,350 --> 00:33:42,070
of the Provincial
Criminal Investigation Department,

609
00:33:42,070 --> 00:33:44,070
and Deputy Director Guo Jianmin

610
00:33:44,070 --> 00:33:45,160
of the municipal police station.

611
00:33:45,160 --> 00:33:46,820
The municipal bureau
will set up the command center.

612
00:33:46,820 --> 00:33:48,480
We're a surveillance ops team formed by

613
00:33:48,480 --> 00:33:49,510
the CIB Nancheng Branch,

614
00:33:49,510 --> 00:33:50,510
the municipal SWAT team,

615
00:33:50,510 --> 00:33:52,510
and the anti-drug team.

616
00:33:52,700 --> 00:33:54,740
Deploy and set up control at 3 P.M.

617
00:34:09,650 --> 00:34:10,960
Reporting to the Command Center.

618
00:34:10,960 --> 00:34:12,480
According to the reconnaissance,

619
00:34:12,480 --> 00:34:13,760
Yatou Pharmaceutical Factory

620
00:34:13,760 --> 00:34:15,760
has three main factory buildings inside.

621
00:34:15,760 --> 00:34:17,719
Each is about 800 square meters.

622
00:34:17,920 --> 00:34:19,800
The largest one is three stories high.

623
00:34:19,800 --> 00:34:21,590
Since they evaded previous inspections,

624
00:34:21,590 --> 00:34:24,400
there should be underground levels
and secret passages.

625
00:34:24,400 --> 00:34:26,389
Based on the topography of Kuangshan,

626
00:34:26,389 --> 00:34:28,090
the technical department has built

627
00:34:28,090 --> 00:34:29,590
a digital model of the factory.

628
00:34:29,590 --> 00:34:30,940
We have formulated corresponding

629
00:34:30,940 --> 00:34:32,610
attack and defense strategies and routes.

630
00:34:32,610 --> 00:34:35,060
Now transmitting to all units.

631
00:34:38,260 --> 00:34:38,870
Received.

632
00:34:39,280 --> 00:34:40,969
Let us know if you need anything.

633
00:34:40,969 --> 00:34:43,800
The Command Center will fully support you.

634
00:34:43,840 --> 00:34:44,570
Understood.

635
00:34:44,670 --> 00:34:46,600
We will act at the designated time.

636
00:34:47,110 --> 00:34:47,969
Pair of threes.

637
00:34:49,150 --> 00:34:50,400
Pair of threes...

638
00:34:51,400 --> 00:34:52,110
Pass.

639
00:34:52,190 --> 00:34:53,150
Pass, right?

640
00:34:53,800 --> 00:34:55,420
Nine, ten, jack, queen, king.

641
00:34:55,420 --> 00:34:56,030
Hello,

642
00:34:56,030 --> 00:34:58,090
the number you dialed is powered off.

643
00:34:58,590 --> 00:34:59,550
I knew you had to pass.

644
00:34:59,550 --> 00:35:00,070
King.

645
00:35:01,480 --> 00:35:02,110
Anyone?

646
00:35:02,710 --> 00:35:03,400
Ace.

647
00:35:03,960 --> 00:35:04,630
Two.

648
00:35:06,400 --> 00:35:07,510
Cheng, where are you going?

649
00:35:07,510 --> 00:35:09,110
I'm going out. You guys play.

650
00:35:21,850 --> 00:35:23,310
I need to see Old Scorpion.

651
00:35:29,210 --> 00:35:30,500
What's the rush?

652
00:35:38,170 --> 00:35:39,290
I want to see Old Scorpion.

653
00:35:39,290 --> 00:35:40,770
Aren't you Old Scorpion?

654
00:35:42,150 --> 00:35:42,840
Boss He,

655
00:35:43,190 --> 00:35:44,630
don't mess with me.

656
00:35:46,410 --> 00:35:48,270
I'm looking for Old Scorpion too.

657
00:35:48,720 --> 00:35:50,380
I haven't been able to see him.

658
00:35:50,810 --> 00:35:52,940
Message Qiu Ye if you need anything.

659
00:35:53,540 --> 00:35:55,220
I did, but she didn't reply.

660
00:35:57,670 --> 00:35:59,230
Maybe she's

661
00:35:59,230 --> 00:36:00,670
in another warehouse

662
00:36:00,670 --> 00:36:01,960
without any signal.

663
00:36:03,200 --> 00:36:04,600
I'll go find her with you?

664
00:36:05,590 --> 00:36:06,280
Forget it.

665
00:36:06,360 --> 00:36:07,360
Too much trouble.

666
00:36:07,590 --> 00:36:08,150
Cheng.

667
00:36:10,360 --> 00:36:11,880
If you're free,

668
00:36:12,630 --> 00:36:13,510
come to my place

669
00:36:14,010 --> 00:36:15,010
for a drink.

670
00:36:16,670 --> 00:36:17,150
Sure.

671
00:36:24,670 --> 00:36:25,400
Cheng.

672
00:36:27,400 --> 00:36:28,670
We haven't had

673
00:36:29,150 --> 00:36:30,920
a calm and quiet talk like this

674
00:36:30,940 --> 00:36:31,770
in a while.

675
00:36:33,400 --> 00:36:35,000
You look tired.

676
00:36:35,800 --> 00:36:36,550
Why?

677
00:36:37,590 --> 00:36:38,360
Stressed?

678
00:36:38,960 --> 00:36:39,920
I'm fine.

679
00:36:40,760 --> 00:36:41,760
It's just that

680
00:36:42,000 --> 00:36:43,660
I haven't been sleeping well.

681
00:36:43,800 --> 00:36:44,600
Thanks, Boss.

682
00:36:49,880 --> 00:36:50,810
Do you regret it?

683
00:36:51,890 --> 00:36:53,200
Regret trying so hard

684
00:36:53,770 --> 00:36:55,370
to climb up the ladder?

685
00:36:56,880 --> 00:36:57,630
Regret?

686
00:37:00,360 --> 00:37:01,690
I regret a lot of things.

687
00:37:03,510 --> 00:37:05,400
You can only be loyal

688
00:37:05,880 --> 00:37:07,230
when there's no way out.

689
00:37:08,590 --> 00:37:09,990
We all went through this.

690
00:37:10,400 --> 00:37:11,070
You are

691
00:37:12,150 --> 00:37:13,560
still too young.

692
00:37:14,190 --> 00:37:14,670
Come on.

693
00:37:23,070 --> 00:37:23,710
Boss He,

694
00:37:24,200 --> 00:37:25,660
what new product are they researching

695
00:37:25,660 --> 00:37:26,910
so tirelessly?

696
00:37:32,590 --> 00:37:33,320
Cheng,

697
00:37:33,670 --> 00:37:35,080
I told you before

698
00:37:35,920 --> 00:37:39,050
that Old Scorpion's biggest trait
is being mysterious.

699
00:37:39,230 --> 00:37:40,070
So,

700
00:37:41,150 --> 00:37:42,520
I never ask questions.

701
00:37:46,280 --> 00:37:47,340
Where is everyone?

702
00:37:50,230 --> 00:37:51,290
Where is everyone?

703
00:37:52,070 --> 00:37:53,510
They all ran away, right?

704
00:38:27,350 --> 00:38:28,480
Qi is looking for me.

705
00:38:36,510 --> 00:38:37,190
Boss He,

706
00:38:37,690 --> 00:38:38,860
stop pretending.

707
00:38:39,130 --> 00:38:40,450
When did they leave?

708
00:38:40,470 --> 00:38:41,430
You must know.

709
00:38:45,440 --> 00:38:46,300
Where are they?

710
00:38:47,690 --> 00:38:48,650
I'm asking you!

711
00:38:48,760 --> 00:38:49,620
Where are they?

712
00:38:49,710 --> 00:38:50,840
I don't know either.

713
00:38:52,000 --> 00:38:53,790
I was just told to guard here

714
00:38:54,030 --> 00:38:55,400
and not let anyone in.

715
00:38:55,650 --> 00:38:56,710
When did this happen?

716
00:38:56,710 --> 00:38:58,310
The night before yesterday.

717
00:39:00,480 --> 00:39:02,480
Looks like they left a long time ago.

718
00:39:02,480 --> 00:39:03,440
But it's fine.

719
00:39:04,030 --> 00:39:04,630
Boss He,

720
00:39:05,150 --> 00:39:06,550
you being here works too.

721
00:39:06,630 --> 00:39:07,630
I just want to ask,

722
00:39:07,680 --> 00:39:08,590
when will you pay me

723
00:39:08,590 --> 00:39:09,800
the three million in commission?

724
00:39:09,800 --> 00:39:10,440
What?

725
00:39:10,580 --> 00:39:12,140
Qi made a deal with me

726
00:39:12,160 --> 00:39:14,210
that as long as I
brought that cop back alive,

727
00:39:14,210 --> 00:39:16,470
he'd pay me three million in commission.

728
00:39:16,740 --> 00:39:18,140
That cop is dead.

729
00:39:18,230 --> 00:39:18,590
Dead?

730
00:39:19,880 --> 00:39:21,270
If he's dead, then you guys killed him.

731
00:39:21,270 --> 00:39:22,110
Not us!

732
00:39:22,250 --> 00:39:24,160
He was alive when we brought him back.

733
00:39:24,160 --> 00:39:25,490
He was still breathing!

734
00:39:26,590 --> 00:39:27,150
Fine.

735
00:39:28,190 --> 00:39:29,720
Then wait for Qi to come back

736
00:39:30,520 --> 00:39:31,070
and have him pay you.

737
00:39:31,070 --> 00:39:31,960
Wait for him?

738
00:39:31,960 --> 00:39:33,840
Do you think I'm an idiot? Look around!

739
00:39:33,840 --> 00:39:35,400
They all ran away!

740
00:39:37,190 --> 00:39:38,710
Calm down.

741
00:39:38,840 --> 00:39:40,510
Once Qi comes back,

742
00:39:40,510 --> 00:39:42,280
I'll ask him what the plan is.

743
00:39:42,280 --> 00:39:43,590
Your next step

744
00:39:43,590 --> 00:39:44,710
has nothing to do with me.

745
00:39:44,710 --> 00:39:46,000
You weren't telling the truth anyway.

746
00:39:46,000 --> 00:39:47,000
I thought

747
00:39:47,060 --> 00:39:48,280
after the Jingang Wharf matter
was settled,

748
00:39:48,280 --> 00:39:50,010
I could easily get my money.

749
00:39:50,030 --> 00:39:51,110
But now?

750
00:39:51,110 --> 00:39:52,590
You made a mess of it.

751
00:39:52,760 --> 00:39:54,590
You guys caused so much trouble!

752
00:39:59,510 --> 00:40:00,110
Bro.

753
00:40:01,570 --> 00:40:03,900
Things didn't go as smoothly
as you think.

754
00:40:03,960 --> 00:40:04,590
Boss He.

755
00:40:08,550 --> 00:40:10,210
Every industry has its rules.

756
00:40:10,360 --> 00:40:12,190
My men and I risked our lives here

757
00:40:12,600 --> 00:40:14,460
just for that commission, right?

758
00:40:14,630 --> 00:40:16,880
Now, you can't let him live it up

759
00:40:16,960 --> 00:40:18,630
while you screw us out of our money.

760
00:40:18,630 --> 00:40:19,510
No way!

761
00:40:23,800 --> 00:40:25,330
You want to run away, right?

762
00:40:26,590 --> 00:40:27,250
No problem.

763
00:40:28,230 --> 00:40:28,960
Come with me.

764
00:40:40,960 --> 00:40:42,220
Let's go get the money.

765
00:40:47,400 --> 00:40:48,460
What are you doing?

766
00:40:48,750 --> 00:40:49,280
Let go.

767
00:40:51,110 --> 00:40:51,840
Let go.

768
00:41:14,300 --> 00:41:15,160
See that?

769
00:41:15,800 --> 00:41:16,760
They all left.

770
00:41:17,800 --> 00:41:19,060
This kind of dirty work

771
00:41:19,880 --> 00:41:21,280
was left for us to handle.

772
00:41:22,150 --> 00:41:23,750
They're on the same side.

773
00:41:26,170 --> 00:41:26,770
Cheng,

774
00:41:28,190 --> 00:41:30,250
you better just follow me from now on.

775
00:41:31,440 --> 00:41:33,400
We are the only two left now.

776
00:41:34,980 --> 00:41:36,240
Two wanted criminals.

777
00:41:37,110 --> 00:41:37,890
Two...

778
00:41:37,920 --> 00:41:39,110
watchdogs.

779
00:41:41,280 --> 00:41:42,080
What's wrong?

780
00:41:42,840 --> 00:41:43,630
Regret it?

781
00:41:44,400 --> 00:41:46,150
It's too late to regret now.

782
00:41:47,550 --> 00:41:48,750
Sorry to trouble you,

783
00:41:48,770 --> 00:41:49,770
but get rid of him.

784
00:42:09,150 --> 00:42:10,360
Team 1 and Team 2,

785
00:42:10,840 --> 00:42:12,320
go up the mountain to Position 1 now.

786
00:42:12,320 --> 00:42:13,310
Team 1 copies.

787
00:42:24,880 --> 00:42:25,920
Surveillance team,

788
00:42:25,920 --> 00:42:26,920
stake out closely

789
00:42:27,030 --> 00:42:28,560
and watch out for sentries.

790
00:42:28,630 --> 00:42:29,230
Copy that.

791
00:43:04,840 --> 00:43:05,440
All right.

792
00:43:05,630 --> 00:43:06,320
Let's bury him here.
